our legal basis for processing your personal data.
We rely on the following legal bases under data protection legislation to process your personal data:
Performance of a contract
: We may process your personal data if it is necessary to perform a contract with you or take steps prior to entering into a contract with you;
Consent
: We may process your personal data because we have obtained your consent to do so. Where you have given us your consent you are free to withdraw your consent at any time;
Legitimate interests
: We may need to process your personal data in a certain way which is justified considering any possible risks to you; and
Legal obligations
: We may need to process your personal data to comply with our legal obligations.
